The function `add_one` exists, but no method is defined for this combination of argument types.

Closest candidates are:
  add_one(<span class="ansi-bright-red-fg">::Union{Float64, Int64}</span>)
<span class="ansi-bright-black-fg">   @</span> <span class="ansi-magenta-fg">Main</span> <span style="text-decoration:underline" class="ansi-bright-black-fg">In[1767]:2</span>
  add_one(<span class="ansi-bright-red-fg">::T</span>) where T&lt;:Number
<span class="ansi-bright-black-fg">   @</span> <span class="ansi-magenta-fg">Main</span> <span style="text-decoration:underline" class="ansi-bright-black-fg">In[1861]:1</span>


